OL,6,FOne teacher was stabbed in the neck
OL,7,Fand airlifted out of school grounds,
OL,8,Faccording to reports.
OL,10,FAnother teacher was injured, and so
OL,11,Fwas a pupil.
OL,13,FDarrel Campbell, a long-serving
OL,14,Fteacher of the school, reportedly
OL,15,Fdisarmed the alleged attacker and put
OL,16,Fher in an armlock ahead of emergency
OL,17,Fservices arriving.
OL,19,FHe is said to not have been harmed
OL,20,Fduring the incident.
