OL,6,F"He probably did what most people
OL,7,Fwould have done in the same situation,
OL,8,Ftry to calm things and restrain people
OL,9,Ffrom making the situation worse.
OL,10,FObviously he's been shaken by the
OL,11,Fwhole experience as of all the staff,
OL,12,Fpupils, parents and so on.
