OL,6,FCarmarthenshire Council leader Darren
OL,7,FPrice, said: "I would like to take
OL,8,Fthis opportunity to praise the
OL,9,Fteachers, staff and pupils at Ysgol
OL,10,FDyffryn Aman for the way they have
OL,11,Fresponded to this shocking incident."
OL,13,FIn a statement posted on the school's
OL,14,Fwebsite, headteacher James Durbridge
OL,15,Fsaid: "Today has been a very difficult
OL,16,Fday.
OL,18,F"It goes without saying that my
OL,19,Fthoughts are with the three
OL,20,Findividuals and their families, who
OL,21,Fhave been affected by today's incident.
