OL,6,F"I wish to commend all staff and
OL,7,Fpupils for their calm and mature
OL,8,Fresponse during today's lockdown. We
OL,9,Fare proud to have witnessed pupils
OL,10,Fembodying the school's core values
OL,11,Fwhile supporting their peers and staff.
OL,13,F"In the immediate aftermath of the
OL,14,Fincident, our priority was to ensure
OL,15,Fthe security of pupils and staff
OL,16,Fwhilst managing the situation and
OL,17,Fcommunicating with those directly
OL,18,Fimpacted."
