OL,6,FThe school went into lockdown after a
OL,7,F"code red" alarm sounded through the
OL,8,FPA system, during which students and
OL,9,Fstaff hid in classrooms.
OL,11,FThe lockdown lasted around four hours
OL,12,Fbetween 11.20am and 3.20pm, resulting
OL,13,Fin a lengthy and anxious wait for
OL,14,Fparents who were seen tearfully
OL,15,Fhugging their children after they
OL,16,Fwalked through the gates once the
OL,17,Fincident had concluded.
